h4. Purpose

The wcm:link tag creates a clickable link to the content rendered by a content node in the repository. You use this just like Grails g:link, but you pass in the path to a content node.

*Example* 

{code}
<wcm:link path="some/uri/path">Click me</wcm:link>
{code}

h4. Description

The supported attributes are:

* path - URI path of the content to link to